{"tid":2096011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬：我上堂同學生討論港獨是體現學術自由","createTime":"2020-07-06T01:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:03:23.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5af7d39d48397a093b9a8633b84e4ba7ee0cc542","tid":2096011,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"被問及第 20 條為何只針對分裂國家的「行為」而沒提及「言論」，資深大律師<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洪</span></strong>回應指，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果只喊港獨口號不會犯法，就如同對別人說「我想殺你」並沒有犯罪，但如果拿著刀說同一句子則可能被視為「意圖謀殺」</span>，故審判時必須考慮情景及動機，不能一概而論。立法會議員梁美芬舉例，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果她在課堂上與學生討論港獨，則可視為體現學術自由，但如果是拿著旗幟叫喊口號，則明顯為「提倡港獨」</span>，便可被控違反《國安法》。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/譚惠珠-國安案交香港審議非必然-即使中央不讓香港審-法理上說得通/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%A4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E9%9D%9E%E5%BF%85%E7%84%B6-%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A9-%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%AA%E5%BE%97%E9%80%9A%2F&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=e71ea2b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%A4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E9%9D%9E%E5%BF%85%E7%84%B6-%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A9-%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%AA%E5%BE%97%E9%80%9A%2F&h=1e4bf01f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/譚惠珠-國安案交香港審議非必然-即使中央不讓香港審-法理上說得通/</a><br />\n尾fun討論港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0baa0a2157021df48e6dc051063c91f666e35b1","tid":2096011,"uid":18477,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:27:01.000Z","msg":"標準任你擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class